1. *Grozno* je što smo morali da odemo ranije nego što smo planirali. (It's terrible that we had to leave earlier than we planned.)

2. Oni su me pogledali sa *groznom* prezirnošću. (They looked at me with contemptuous disgust.)

3. Ona je sebi nanela *grozne* povrede. (She inflicted severe injuries upon herself.)

4. *Grozno* je koliko je vremena prošlo od njegovog poslednjeg poziva. (It's terrible how much time has passed since his last call.)

5. On je bio *grozan* prema njoj i njenoj porodici. (He was awful to her and her family.)